    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category</strong>: Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Fujou Clan, 4+<br /><strong>Description</strong>: You have awakened the ability to share your life force with other people. You gain the following:</p><ul><li>increase your constitution ability score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</li><li>You become able to learn and cast jutsu with the medical keyword.</li><li>When using your <strong>Accursed Existence</strong> Clan feature, you can forfeit healing yourself to instead heal one willing creature within 5ft of you.</li><li>As part of a short rest, you may spend up to half your hit dice or chakra dice, giving them to another creature that is also taking a short rest.</li></ul>",
